<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ms">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Meow Lyrics | Muzik Di Hujung Jari</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background-color: #FFFDF0; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
        .paw-print { opacity: 0.1; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col text-gray-800">

    <nav class="glass sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-yellow-100 p-4">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-black text-yellow-500 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-white p-1 rounded-lg">🐾</span> MEOWLYRICS
            </a>
            <div class="flex gap-6 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">
                <a href="/" class="text-yellow-600 border-b-2 border-yellow-400 pb-1">HOME</a>
                <a href="/account" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-yellow-500 transition">ACCOUNT</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="py-16 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <span class="bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 inline-block">MEOW-ZIK TERBAIK</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">Cari lirik lagu <br><span class="text-yellow-500">kegemaranmu</span> di sini.</h1>
            
            <form action="/" method="GET" class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto group">
                <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Tulis tajuk lagu atau nama artis..." 
                    class="w-full p-5 pl-14 rounded-3xl border-2 border-white shadow-2xl focus:border-yellow-400 focus:ring-0 outline-none transition-all text-lg"
                    value="<%= carian || '' %>">
                <span class="absolute left-5 top-5 text-2xl group-focus-within:scale-110 transition">🔍</span>
                <button class="absolute right-3 top-3 bg-yellow-400 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-yellow-500 transition">Cari</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="paw-print text-6xl top-10 left-10 rotate-12">🐾</div>
        <div class="paw-print text-6xl bottom-5 right-20 -rotate-12">🐾</div>
    </header>

    <main class="p-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full flex-grow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div> 
                <%= carian ? 'Hasil Carian' : 'Lirik Popular' %>
            </h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium"><%= lagu.length %> Lagu Dijumpai</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <% lagu.forEach(l => { %>
                <a href="/lagu/<%= l.slug %>" class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-[32px] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-yellow-50 flex flex-col justify-between h-44 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <h3 class="font-black text-xl text-gray-800 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition"><%= l.tajuk %></h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium"><%= l.penyanyi %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center relative z-10">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-yellow-600 bg-yellow-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Lihat Lirik</span>
                        <span class="text-2xl opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500">🐾</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-24 h-24 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition"></div>
                </a>
            <% }) %>
        </div>

        <% if(lagu.length == 0) { %>
            <div class="text-center py-20 bg-white rounded-[40px] shadow-inner border-2 border-dashed border-yellow-200">
                <span class="text-6xl mb-4 block">😿</span>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-widest">Maaf, lirik tiada dalam pangkalan data</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-20 pt-16 pb-8 px-6 rounded-t-[50px] relative">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-yellow-400">🐾 MEOWLYRICS</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Website lirik lagu paling comel di Malaysia. Kami mengumpulkan beribu lirik lagu khas untuk anda pencinta muzik dan kucing.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="md:text-right">
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">Navigasi Pantas</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-400">Utama</a>
                    <a href="/account" class="hover:text-yellow-400">Akaun Saya</a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-yellow-400">Hubungi Kami</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-medium">
                © 2026 Credits : <span class="text-yellow-500 font-black tracking-widest">MEOW LYRICS</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
